                                                                                                                                    <p>While smartwatches are taking their places on the wrists of more people, I'm content to stay with a classic Casio design, the F-91W. Here's why it will take more than some fancy features to pry it off my arm.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Tue, 23 Sep 2025 15:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/why-i-use-this-classic-casio-watch-instead-of-a-smartwatch/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[AdGuard’s New Filtering Engine Catches a Lot More Ads]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/adguard-new-filtering-engine-catches-a-lot-more-ads/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jorge A. Aguilar]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/agnar-the-adguard-mascot-in-front-of-a-green-gradient-radial-background.jpg" length="121" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Web]]></category><category><![CDATA[ads]]></category><description><![CDATA[
